466
00:34:04,670 --> 00:34:07,840
-When is your mom coming?
-Like, four, I think.

467
00:34:15,100 --> 00:34:16,680
Oh man.

468
00:34:18,310 --> 00:34:21,100
-Hey, Baek Dal-shik!
